- OPTIONS is generally provided by the framework for any mapped endpoint, so it is acceptable.
- All other HTTP methods (POST, PUT, DELETE, PATCH) are not mapped for this path, so they are not acceptable.
- There is no class-level prefix in the provided code, so the full path remains exactly /consumer/notifications, with no path parameters.
